HEADWORD: Astacus
<hw>As"ta*cus</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>astacus</ets> a crab, Gr. <?/.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
